  "short_description": "Wild Explorer takes you on an immersive journey deep into the wild. Capture stunning photos of wildlife, explore ancient monuments, and uncover hidden secrets. Use your torch to navigate the darkness and complete your exploration book with every discovery. Are you ready for the adventure?",
