  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration, Adventure, and Mystery in an Open World!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to uncover the deepest secrets of nature? <strong>Wild Explorer</strong> invites you into a world of discovery, survival, and mystery. From remote forests to ancient ruins, every corner hides a new story. Prepare your camera, follow the traces of nature, and reveal forgotten secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Realistic Photography Mechanics</strong><br>Capture the rarest animals and historic monuments in the wild, adding them to your explorer’s journal. Improve your observation skills, seize the perfect moment, and complete your discovery book!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/1c0d1659b8b86ded0bdb7bf840da8024.poster.avif?t=1752886463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/1c0d1659b8b86ded0bdb7bf840da8024.webm?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/1c0d1659b8b86ded0bdb7bf840da8024.mp4?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛺ <strong>Manage Time and Survive</strong><br>Time is in your hands! <strong>Rest in your tent</strong> to turn night into day, explore in the darkness, or use daylight to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/019a7f89615a958e22b0de79173083c8.poster.avif?t=1752886463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/019a7f89615a958e22b0de79173083c8.webm?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/019a7f89615a958e22b0de79173083c8.mp4?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ <strong>Vast Open World and Map Navigation</strong><br>From treacherous swamps to shadowy forests, abandoned temples to towering peaks… Each region has its own ecosystem and hidden mysteries! Use the map carefully to avoid losing your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/6c546619f4b4a7df9cb41743970efe38.poster.avif?t=1752886463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/6c546619f4b4a7df9cb41743970efe38.webm?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/6c546619f4b4a7df9cb41743970efe38.mp4?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗣️ <strong>Interact with NPCs and Discover Hidden Clues</strong><br>Talk to mysterious characters in the area to learn the locations of lost monuments. Your choices shape your adventure, and every discovery brings you closer to great secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/a675a8e451cdefdaa0fb9c10f8bbf57e.poster.avif?t=1752886463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/a675a8e451cdefdaa0fb9c10f8bbf57e.webm?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/a675a8e451cdefdaa0fb9c10f8bbf57e.mp4?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📜 <strong>Ancient Relics and Forgotten Legends</strong><br>The forest holds more than just nature—<strong>traces of forgotten civilizations</strong> await! The <strong>Legendary Sword</strong>, lost tombs, and tales from the depths of history are waiting to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/d58aa8873ce490f92ffa0efdd5214387.poster.avif?t=1752886463\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/d58aa8873ce490f92ffa0efdd5214387.webm?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496690/extras/d58aa8873ce490f92ffa0efdd5214387.mp4?t=1752886463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to become a true explorer?</strong><br>📸 Explore, document your findings, and reveal nature’s greatest mysteries!</p>",
